          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36895665/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36895665/" class="">第25页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/whoselove/" class=" " title="老糖酸菜牛肉面">老糖酸菜牛肉面</a>
                (练习不经意的仁慈与美德)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="36895665">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">对于一位知识分子来说，成为思维的精英，比成为导的精英更为重要。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-01-02 00:44</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
